canonical:
  title: 二月日特蒙上恩賜臣老母米穀仍除臣官職臣不勝感激詣闕陳謝道中率爾寓興兼東郡守曺大虛
  author: 兪好仁
  language: lzh
  text: 淸東畔主人公一絆簪纓蕙帳空卄載詩壇曾割據如今盡屬使君封
  rtl: true
  vertical: true
lzh_formatted:
  title: 二月日特蒙上恩賜臣老母米穀仍除臣官職臣不勝感激詣闕陳謝道中率爾寓興兼東郡守曺大虛
  author: 兪好仁
  language: lzh
  text: 淸東畔主人公。一絆簪纓蕙帳空。卄載詩壇曾割據。如今盡屬使君封。
korean:
  title: 2월 어느날 특별히 주상의 은혜를 입어 신의 늙은 어머니에게 쌀과 곡식을 주시고 이어 신에게 관직을 제수하시니 신은 감격을 이기지 못하여 대궐 앞에 감사를 올리려 가는 도중에 생각나는 대로 흥을 읊고 군수 조대허에게 보낸다
  author: 유호인
  language: kor
  text: |-
    맑은 뇌수 그 동녘에 살고 있는 주인공이
    벼슬에 한번 얽매이자 혜초 장막 비어 있고
    스무 해 시단에서 일찍이 겨루던 것
    이제에 이르러선 사군에게 다 맡기오
  url: https://db.itkc.or.kr/dir/item?itemId=BT#dir/node?dataId=ITKC_BT_1365A_1460_010_0070&viewSync=OT
  footnotes: []
english:
  title: Sent on the Way to Court to Offer Thanks for the Royal Grace of Providing Grain to My Elderly Mother and Conferring Official Rank Upon Me in the Second Month—Composed Extemporaneously and Addressed to Magistrate Cho Dae-heo
  author: Yu Ho-in
  language: eng
  text: |-
    On the clear waters of the eastern bank dwells the master of this place—
    Once bound by office, the fragrant chamber of verse lies empty.
    These twenty years I held sway in poetry's domain,
    Yet now I yield it all to the magistrate's command.
  footnotes:
    - The 'clear waters of the eastern bank' may allude to a retreat from worldly affairs, here juxtaposed with the speaker's appointment to office.
    - The 'fragrant chamber' (蕙帳) references a poetic sanctuary; its emptiness suggests the poet's departure from the literary circles he once dominated.
    - The twenty years of poetic achievement represent the author's former life of scholarly pursuits before taking official position.
